view.text:
2 bedroom, 1 bath apartment located in the heart of the Inner Richmond District between Geary and Clement Streets. Street facing. Gated building with washer and dryer on site.

Inlaid hardwood floors throughout. Eat-in kitchen. Street facing. Recessed lighting, Dishwasher, Decorator styling, Stainless steel appliances, White built-in Plantation shutters, quartz counter tops, marble shower, soft close cabinets, pendant light.

Secure parking for 2 available.
Trash and water included.

Walk to 1 block to Sunday Farmers’ Market, great restaurants - Le Soleil, Eats, Burma Super Star, Cafe Bunn Mi, Arsicault, Dragon Beaux, Brother’s BBQ, Good Luck Dim Sum, Toy Boat, B* Star, Mandalay, Shubert’s Bakery, among others. 

Close to Golden Gate Park, USF, library, groceries, banks, Green Apple Books, public transit, great schools and other amenities.

No smoking.
No animals.

First month + security deposit
